precis:
Enactment of the PROVINCIAL EMERGENCIES FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 22 -
which DECLARES a provincial emergency to be of concern to the federal
government and authorizes the provision of financial assistance in respect
thereof (severe winter storm and fooding in B.C., late December 1996).
